{
  "stem": "22047.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Finally, when I saw most of my guys had gotten back, I crawled back and was able to get out of there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the people in my company assumed I was dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so I came back, and I received a welcoming [LAUGHS] committee when I got back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Boy, that was-- that was scary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was really scary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Really.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- so we-- we assumed a move then to this area that we occupied from latter part of February to when we assumed the-- the attack in March.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so from the-- which I described before, this business of-- of being pinned down on the side of the hill and-- and running down and capturing these Germans-- we went on and lost-- lost these folks from snipers and neutralizing the snipers, and then went on toward the Siegfried Line.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we ran into a lot of-- lot of small battles along the way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One in particular, we were heading down this, I guess you call it a saddle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was a U-shaped junction, I guess, of a valley.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were heading down there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And two tanks across the valley started firing their guns at us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and the sound of an 88 is really traumatic, because you hear the-- you hear the-- if you-- if you aren't hit by one, you hear it bang over your head.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then you hear the gun going off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're so fast, just several thousand feet per second those rounds go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they're that big around, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we-- we got as low to the ground as we could get and and survived most of that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the tanks pulled away, and we continued on with our chasing the Germans across Alsace-Lorraine.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
